<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en">
  <%- include("./partials/head.ejs") %>

  <body id="account">
    <%- include("./partials/header.ejs") %>
    <section id="acct-top">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need an Enrolled Agent?</h2>
        <h5>
          Is your Tax- Preparer a professional licensed at the Federal level by
          the IRS in the United States.
        </h5>
        <p>
          We are here to provide you with the best set of Enrolled Agents for
          $0. <br />
          You can also get a free consultation from your Tax-Preparer or any of
          the firms listed on our Website. Provide us with the necessary
          information by filling the form below. With the information provided,
          we can help you discover an Enrolled Agent who's just right for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="acct-form" class="container">
      <div class="acct-form-top">
        <h3>Your Contact Information</h3>
        <p>
          Provide your basic contact details, so that we can respond with your
          verification results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="main-form">
        <div class="first-flex">
          <input
            type="text"
            name="first-name"
            id="f-name"
            placeholder="First Name*"
          />
          <input
            type="text"
            name="last-name"
            id="l-name"
            placeholder="Last Name*"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="second-flex">
          <input
            type="text"
            name="email"
            id="email"
            placeholder="Email Address"
          />
          <input
            type="number"
            name="phone-number"
            id="p-number"
            placeholder="Phone Number*"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="third-flex">
          <div class="inner-flex">
            <input type="text" name="city" id="city" placeholder="City*" />
            <input type="number" name="" id="" placeholder="zip Code*" />
          </div>
          <div class="state-flex">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="state"
              id="state"
              placeholder="Select a State"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fourth-flex">
          <input
            type="text"
            name="help"
            id="help"
            placeholder="I Need Help With"
          />
          <input
            type="text"
            name="text"
            id="text-class"
            placeholder="Tax Classification"
          />
        </div>
        <small>Relevant Details about Your Needs</small>
        <div class="text-area">
          <textarea name="text" id="text"></textarea>
          <input
            type="text"
            name="input-method"
            id="method"
            placeholder="Preferred Input Method"
          />
          <p>
            <input type="radio" name="radio" id="radio" />
            I am comfortable working virtually with a tax professional
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="b-tons">
          <a href="" class="b-ton">Connect Me With a Local EA</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="last-section" class="container">
      <p>
        Why is this service free?
        <br />
        Our goal is to put at your disposal the wealth of resources of Enrolled Agents. The 
        connection is free to  make it easier for you locate a certified Tax Preparer.
      </p>

