        in handling income tax returns for individuals as well as more complex
        tax returns for families, nonprofit corporations, and businesses of all
        sizes. All of the CPAs in our referal network are required to provide us
        with proof of a valid license in good standing.
      </p> -->
    </section>

    <!-- footer section -->
    <%- include("./partials/footer.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
